00:34:20,380 --> 00:34:20,830
Whose workshop is this?

546
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:21,830
Mine.

547
00:34:23,050 --> 00:34:25,040
Which room will I stay in?

548
00:34:25,350 --> 00:34:27,290
You'll stay there then.

549
00:34:27,950 --> 00:34:29,430
Whose room is this?

550
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:30,630
This is mine.

551
00:34:32,950 --> 00:34:33,780
Nice.

552
00:34:33,810 --> 00:34:35,810
This workshop's quite well-built.

553
00:34:35,810 --> 00:34:37,870
Much better than Symphony Workshop.

554
00:34:38,220 --> 00:34:39,450
If you like it here,

555
00:34:39,470 --> 00:34:40,640
you can join us too.

556
00:34:41,530 --> 00:34:42,350
Shangyu.

557
00:34:42,390 --> 00:34:44,000
You can also join the workshop.

558
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:45,410
If you don't mind

559
00:34:45,430 --> 00:34:46,620
tarnishing your master status...

560
00:34:46,620 --> 00:34:48,020
Hold on.

561
00:34:48,140 --> 00:34:49,830
When you first established this workshop,

562
00:34:49,830 --> 00:34:51,430
I was the first one to sign up.

563
00:34:51,890 --> 00:34:53,980
Then count me in.

564
00:34:54,110 --> 00:34:55,240
I want to be with Jin.

565
00:34:55,260 --> 00:34:57,160
It's a deal.

566
00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:58,480
If you join,

567
00:34:58,510 --> 00:35:00,430
the others will love it.

568
00:35:00,990 --> 00:35:02,300
Fei?

569
00:35:02,550 --> 00:35:03,240
Monkey! Biao!

570
00:35:03,240 --> 00:35:04,640
Come now! See who's back!

571
00:35:05,670 --> 00:35:06,550
-Fei!
-Monkey!

572
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:08,950
Fei!

573
00:35:08,980 --> 00:35:10,050
-Eleven! Monkey!
